      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wisch turra Dſelfi ta\natt ka Salmus/ un Watru ka\nprauleifchn Kohlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne kahda Bulta winnu\nistrecks/ Lingv Akmini irr win-\nam ta patt ka Ruggaji.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tahs leelas Bruknas\nrr winſch par Ruggajeem/ un\npfmeij to iſwiktn Schkehu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Appakſch winna gull afi\nkinini/ un winſch iſplattahs\nahr afteem Galleem/ ta patt ka\nahr Dubteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winſch darra/ ka tee Dsit-\nini wehrd ka Pohds/ un fajauz\nJuhzn/ ka weenu Apteekeza\nalivi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pakkaf few apſkaidro\ninsch to Zeku/ ka fchkeet tohs\nfittumus firmus eſofchus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wirg Semines ne neeka\ninnam lihdsinajams/ winſch irr\nddihts bes Bihjaſchanaſ buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winſch nizzina wiﬀn/ kas\nigsts irr/ winſch irr par Rehni-\npahr wiﬀeem lepneem Behr-\nem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "wisfas Leetas eespehji/ un ne kah-\ndas Dohnas irr no tewim ap-\nflehptas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas tas buhtu/ kas to\nDeewa Vadohmu gribbetu ne-\nprattigi apflehpt. Tadeht es\ncfun runnajs/ fo es ne eſimu fa-\nprattis/ tahdas Leetas/ kas\npreekſch man wiﬀai brihnigas\nbija/ fo es ne finnaju.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Klaufi jelle/ un es runna-\nschu/ es waizaschu tew/ un tu\npainahzi mann.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ar paschahm Aufim eſimu\nes tewi dsirdejs/ un uu manna\nAzz tew arrtdsan reds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht es few turrohs par\nnofeedſigu/ un febehlojoſs pahr\nto eekſch Pibſchleem un Pelneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz kad tas KUNGS\nfchohs Wahrdus us Jjabu bij\nrunnajs/ tad tazzija tas KUNGS\nus Geliwafu to Teemaniteri:\nEs eſimu tohti eedufmojees prett\ntewi/ un prett farveem diwi\nDrangeem/ jo juhs ne effat pa-\nreisi runnajcht no mannim/ itt\nka mans Kalps Jjabs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht nemmeetees tepti-\nnus Wehrſchus/ un feptinus\nAnnus/ un eita pee manna Kal-\npa Jjaba/ un uppurejeet Dedsa-\nmo·Uppuens preekſch jums/ un\nleezeet mannu Kalpn Jjabu\npreekſch jums luhgt/ jo es us-\nluhſoschn winan/ ka es jums ne\ndarru pehz juhfas Geckibas/ jo\njuhs ne eſtat pareisi no mannim\nrunnajſchi/ ka mans Kalps J-\njabs.\n"
    }
  ],
